10 years married. 18 years dating. 3 kids. 1 dog. And a whole lotta love. Here’s 10 fun facts about us!
1. We met when I was 18 and Bryce was 16 at a kickback I was throwing at my parents house. #cougar
2. We broke up 2 times in the first 3 years of dating and then realized we didn’t wanna do that anymore 🤪.
3. We have VERY opposite personalities (bet you couldn’t tell, huh?! 😜🤣). 
4. We moved out of town into our first apartment together in 2010.
5. That apartment was the same apartment complex the Dirty John incident happened 😳.
6. We’ve lived in 4 different cities together.
7. We made the 3 cutest kids…Boston, Kollyns, and Kampbell.
8. We rented a house in Bakersfield for 4 years that had carpet in the bathroom and now we bought it and are renovating it and turning it into an Airbnb called #hortonhotel.
9. We never planned on working together but now that we have for the last 3 years, we never want it to be any different. 
10. We almost went on a trip for our 10th anniversary but decided we would rather spend it with the ones who make us the happiest and have been there for us through it all.
#HorTEN
10 hour party cut down to 1 minute #HorTEN 🎉 We can officially say we’re Fancy Like @walkerhayes #ahhh #corememory #10yearanniversary

working with ms @krista.horton has been the most amazing experience ever and spending the last few days with her was the icing on the cake. she is beautiful, loving, and the true definition of kindness.

for those who don’t know i’m on a mission to bring back kindness through service of others. kindness is easy and ms krista lives by its definition every single day. if the world was filled with people like her, well id be out of a job 😜

when you shop her collection this month you’re helping me help others. 100% of the net profits will be donated to The Global Family and The Daughters Project to help them build a new safe haven for victims of human trafficking. 

the world can be a brighter more loving place, despite our differences, if we just choose to live like ms krista.

thank you for shopping with me and making the world a place we all want to live!!! 

and remember, be kind to someone today, it’s all that truly matters.

Hayden & Tatum take Stagecoach 2023 👯‍♀️🤠 a few tips we took away from the trip: take your bestie cuz that way you’re bound to have a good time no matter what, bring an insulated cup to keep your drinks cold cuz it’s HOT and the ice will melt fast, bring comfy shoes (we didn’t and had major ragrets), go one day right when it opens at noon so you can explore without the crowd, and most of all just know you will have the BEST time cuz everyone there is so nice and having so much fun! We had a blast getting ready every day! Our outfits are from @pinklily’s newest desert collection! #pinklilypartner #stagecoach #stagecoach2023
